#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:38
msgid "Differences from GPU Implementation"
msgstr "与GPU实现的差异"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:40
msgid ""
"The `flash_attn_with_kvcache` interface on NPU is semantically consistent"
" with the GPU FA3 version in terms of API parameters. The key differences"
" are:"
msgstr "NPU上的`flash_attn_with_kvcache`接口在API参数上与GPU FA3版本语义一致。主要差异如下："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:42
msgid ""
"**Unsupported features on NPU FA3**: Sliding window attention, RoPE, "
"ALiBi, Softcapping, and FP8 quantization are not yet supported."
msgstr "**NPU FA3不支持的功能**：滑动窗口注意力、RoPE、ALiBi、Softcapping和FP8量化暂不支持。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:43
msgid ""
"**Graph capture**: The tiling of `flash_attn_with_kvcache` is processed "
"on the host side and is currently being optimized. It does not support "
"ACL graph capture (i.e., cannot be captured into a computational graph "
"for acceleration). Please use `enforce_eager=True` when enabling FA3."
msgstr "**图捕获**：`flash_attn_with_kvcache`的tiling在主机侧处理，目前正在优化中。不支持ACL图捕获（即无法捕获到计算图中进行加速）。启用FA3时请使用`enforce_eager=True`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:45
msgid "Hardware Requirements"
msgstr "硬件要求"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:47
msgid ""
"FA3 currently requires Ascend Atlas A2 and A3 inference products NPUs. We"
" will support other NPUs in the future."
msgstr "FA3目前需要Ascend Atlas A2和A3推理产品NPU。未来将支持其他NPU。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:50
msgid "Software Requirements"
msgstr "软件要求"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:52
msgid ""
"FA3 requires the `flash_attn_npu` package, which provides the "
"`flash_attn_npu_v3` module with the `flash_attn_with_kvcache` operator."
msgstr "FA3需要`flash_attn_npu`包，该包提供包含`flash_attn_with_kvcache`算子的`flash_attn_npu_v3`模块。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:54
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:56
msgid ""
"Install the `flash_attn_npu` wheel package refer to: "
"<https://github.com/MinghuasLab/flash-attention-"
"npu/blob/main/README.md#installation>."
msgstr "安装`flash_attn_npu` wheel包，请参考：<https://github.com/MinghuasLab/flash-attention-npu/blob/main/README.md#installation>。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:58
msgid "Enabling Flash Attention 3"
msgstr "启用Flash Attention 3"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:60
msgid "To enable FA3, you need to:"
msgstr "要启用FA3，您需要："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:62
msgid ""
"Set the environment variable `export VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT=1` to enable "
"batch invariant mode"
msgstr "设置环境变量`export VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT=1`以启用batch invariant模式"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/flash_attention.md:63
msgid ""
"Specify the attention backend as `FLASH_ATTN` via the LLM parameter "
"`attention_backend=\"FLASH_ATTN\"`"
msgstr "通过LLM参数`attention_backend=\"FLASH_ATTN\"`将注意力后端指定为`FLASH_ATTN`"

